        <li>Kingfisher: <a href="https://bbcdn.nouse.co.uk/file/nouseSiteAssets/logo/kingfisher-1307-797.png">PNG</a>, <a href="https://bbcdn.nouse.co.uk/file/nouseSiteAssets/logo/kingfisher.svg">SVG</a>, <a href="https://bbcdn.nouse.co.uk/file/nouseSiteAssets/logo/kingfisher.tiff">TIFF</a>, <a href="https://bbcdn.nouse.co.uk/file/nouseSiteAssets/logo/Kingfisher.ai">Adobe Illustrator</a></li>
